{"tid":429802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足同我一樣 同女朋友之間冇信任","createTime":"2017-10-09T09:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T14:46:32.000Z","uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c90f9edf1d99a649ede963d040fe8f64994666d0","tid":429802,"uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我同女朋友以前都試過偷食 <br />\n以為講晒出黎會冇野<br />\n點知係兩個人心入面都留低左條刺<br />\n<br />\n每當佢冇覆whatapp我就以為佢去左偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我冇覆佢 唔搵佢 <br />\n佢就以為我去左搵第二個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地都係今日先為依件事嘈<br />\n結果就係兩個人都唔信任大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打同我地一樣 係會猜忌對方<br />\n咁樣你地又點行落去 定分左手"},{"pid":"5cd2b9ecc965adfdd43af3e4982b3eff8c1df5fd","tid":429802,"uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5be1640a5a0679028ce3d6e0e096eb8e2cdfa57","tid":429802,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"出嚟認真咁坐低傾下個問題試下解決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然要大家坦認咁傾先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最重要心平氣和<br />\n傾完都冇解決到個問題你兩個倒不如分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a707066c64d371f59ee16f65cda77532d6fa784c","tid":429802,"uid":73785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"哂氣，分手啦"},{"pid":"38698b0a97cfa05732bcd5ae4a352402b71b3113","tid":429802,"uid":19838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:55:57.000Z","msg":"返唔到轉頭架喇 分手啦"},{"pid":"69b057cf61dab61771f24d8b04f0580cf136c7c3","tid":429802,"uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"